1f4589b647f286ea2dbcd8e75315541e","tid":162824,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T00:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n人無恥便無敵，有咁易香港就好快獨立到啦<br />\n最起碼暴政之下會有更多人醒<br />\n唔係689，以前邊有咁多「黃絲」出現？</blockquote><br />\n最弊大部份所謂醒都係諗移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n深圳騰籠換鳥果陣都叫養到班原居民發過豬頭<br />\n香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國人唔當你中國人<br />\n英國更加唔洗講"},{"pid":"bdb8ea7a8b7051e92675bb994d96c19cb297a353","tid":162824,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T00:30:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>林病上台搞廿三<br />\n傾都唔使傾 佔中都照立<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n曾俊華做會傾又點？立咗法最終解釋權喺人大到，鐘意點僭建都得<br />\n不如攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n為咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n懲罰港豬 , 抗爭個陣啲港豬就落井下石罵人搞事 , 咁不如大家攬炒"},{"pid":"f5452bfc049ccd13025d8a2770085d0b9686b54b","tid":162824,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T00:30:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日話焦土 好喇 焦左四年喇 有咩分別？</blockquote><br />\n懷疑班焦土撚一係5毛一係就on9<br />\n焦土個前題起碼人要識對抗<br />\n仆你個街宜家香港人撚會對抗咩<br />\n咁對中央根本就係一個好時機推23條"},{"pid":"55fec059a6860b9eba2f9c8830c60d00d343bf8c","tid":162824,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T00:36:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>林鄭選到, 香港又咪一樣投降<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n689暴政路線vs溫水煮蛙路線<br />\n雖然結局都係死但後者大鑊啲</blockquote><br />\n看得自己那麼高,睇下3義士判監後港豬既回應啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正想咁講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真睇完我都灰咗<br />\n不過本土派同勇武抗爭嘅思想係雨革後出現，唔係因為暴政，會有咁多人願意出嚟反抗？<br />\n雖然仆街港豬未來應該仲係大多數但醒得幾多得幾多"},{"pid":"a2c4e7989c1d9c3080543938b12018d06fa370ac","tid":162824,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T00:38:56.000Z","msg":"咪一樣要返工"},{"pid":"b9f77b77a400e22db6a6027b0d5d031219e96ea1","tid":162824,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T00:39:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日話焦土 好喇 焦左四年喇 有咩分別？</blockquote><br />\n我就覺得而家已經夠焦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但好多人仲覺得冇事仲未係焦土喎"},{"pid":"4aac4a29eaa6cd8676a5b0db3bd7047c25f29b14","tid":162824,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T00:40:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪一樣要返工</blockquote><br />\n冇得返工香港人會暴動㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aec337d293098ed532a26a7a1c0b0994d220635","tid":162824,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T00:44:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n人無恥便無敵，有咁易香港就好快獨立到啦<br />\n最起碼暴政之下會有更多人醒<br />\n唔係689，以前邊有咁多「黃絲」出現？</blockquote><br />\n最弊大部份所謂醒都係諗移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n深圳騰籠換鳥果陣都叫養到班原居民發過豬頭<br />\n香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國人唔當你中國人<br />\n英國更加唔洗講</blockquote><br />\n總有一堆移唔到/唔捨得睇住香港仆街嘅人嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff543cb2d0d2bbbb3c6f7f21dfd730d2d7e3e3c9","tid":162824,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T00:56:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n人無恥便無敵，有咁易香港就好快獨立到啦<br />\n最起碼暴政之下會有更多人醒<br />\n唔係689，以前邊有咁多「黃絲」出現？</blockquote><br />\n最弊大部份所謂醒都係諗移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n深圳騰籠換鳥果陣都叫養到班原居民發過豬頭<br />\n香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國人唔當你中國人<br />\n英國更加唔洗講</blockquote><br />\n總有一堆移唔到/唔捨得睇住香港仆街嘅人嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n醒左又可以點<br />\n我有時寧願自己乜都唔知做隻港豬好過依家日日望住個痴撚線嘅香港"},{"pid":"2fc5e0c52e1f1e2f5b2d29a1bf71f2bef765b094","tid":162824,"uid":2013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T00:57:01.000Z","msg":"好多人信曾俊華咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0b769b5a04ab826e523b0acc91e8ef0d30a0c7","tid":162824,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T00:57:34.000Z","msg":"林病選既話你又有乜大計？<br />\n699在任時你又係邊？"},{"pid":"0f9dc3dba74f6744b53000ae479be2c2fb54ccea","tid":162824,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T01:03:12.000Z","msg":"品客必勝"},{"pid":"c3ce00c5bf42c2f7aae7facaaa2432342566da88","tid":162824,"uid":23649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T01:30:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>林病選既話你又有乜大計？<br />\n699在任時你又係邊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鍵盤戰士死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"881d0539c328d10c7367cb762f216cba5e21e58e","tid":162824,"uid":43060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T01:46:15.000Z","msg":"儲定錢移民啦 過多30年 到時你就蚛蟈一部分架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5db8a79f2f9d530c671d5798c10c483f74c2bfb","tid":162824,"uid":91892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T01:51:58.000Z","msg":"林病中定薯片中其實根本無分別，呢兩個選中嘅點都奶共奶到傻，薯片只係形象工程做得好，班港豬見到就流晒口水當佢神咁拜。<br />\n胡官係香港唯一出路，但機會相當渺茫。"},{"pid":"97bd2b4d93ef281f121a499e22b4136b9f3e123f","tid":162824,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T01:52:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當所有人都知道香港人一定唔會反抗時，溫水煮蛙遠比暴力施政輕鬆，點解唔揀前者。但我寧願焦土，全香港人一齊中伏，睇住班所謂中產藍絲一齊死最開心</blockquote><br />\n將來打WW3核戰真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee37a67bd79822022c26002c028f22c5bdfbbda","tid":162824,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T01:57:34.000Z","msg":"邊個做分別唔大，反正香港人已經被統戰"}]}